* Zyber cocked her head, she had known about the major changes but nothing 
about neutral factions. Especially powerful ones.
Her knowledge was limited, she knew.*

" Um...I am not sure. I guess there might be a few. The Alliance base 
was...or is under attack.
The reconstruction on the Ark has comensed...but I doubt that will do much.
Um...Hell Beast has returned, and it seems...Oh, yes. Black Arachnia(sorry 
if I spelled it wrong) is now commanding the Predacons...so far.
The Maximals had captured a few Predacons. Um...and a few bots have died.
Anything else?"

* she watched Blaster carefully.*
